reviewText: Interesting. Just talk a hot shower after watching this DVD, LOL.
This is one of my favorite parasite videos from the Discovery Channel ring and All I can say right now, is that I wish they would put it back up for sale so I could buy it at a reasonable price!
I absolutely love showing this dvd to my class.  It is one of my favorites because students are completely enthralled as well as completely "freaked" out.  :^D
